{"tid":2429235,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"［I/A] 《Last Cloudia 最後的克勞迪亞》- [48]DR.STONE 復刻 抽爆佢！","createTime":"2021-03-02T07:08:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T07:12:06.000Z","uid":211904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6c45f3b8a81933738ee820ccbe9ead17858a3967","tid":2429235,"uid":211904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QYHgfQp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQYHgfQp.png&h=46385993&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官方網站 : <a href=\"https://www.lastcloudia.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lastcloudia.com%2F&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA51eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=a54ae859\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.lastcloudia.com/</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/lastcloudia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flastcloudia&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA51eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=09dc724b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/lastcloudia</a><br />\nYouTube: <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RfalH3BkpeA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRfalH3BkpeA&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA51eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=678c2b19\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RfalH3BkpeA</a><br />\n\t<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n《最後的奇洛迪亞》是滿載了我們都認為是 &ldquo;有趣&rdquo; 的 RPG 元素的作品。故事劇情、表現手法、背景音樂、戰鬥、像素畫、育成、彩蛋隱藏要素 -- 這裏每一個的元素，我們都堅持了我們對遊戲的執着去創作出來。但我們認為這些也都只是為了能享受這個名為《最後的奇洛迪亞》的世界的要素。<br />\n如果能讓各位玩家可以享受 &rdquo;再邁進一步世界就變得更廣闊&rdquo; 這個 RPG 所具有的本來的魅力的話，即使是一點點也好，那便是我們最大的幸福了。<br />\n由於遊戲剛推出，應該還有很多未成熟的部分。不單止是我們想製作的，還有我們應該要製作的部分也有很多。就像在旅途上的 Kyle 和 Ray 他們不斷成長一樣，《最後的奇洛迪亞》這個作品也會一起不斷成長，希望各位玩家也願意陪伴我們一起見證和分享這個成長的旅程。<br />\n  <br />\n2019 年 4 月 15 日<br />\n《最後的奇洛迪亞》製作人 篠子 裕<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">新手須知(睇左先問):</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=35735&amp;snA=651\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D35735%26snA%3D651&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA51eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=bcbc6727\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=35735&amp;snA=651</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=35735&amp;snA=1157&amp;tnum=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D35735%26snA%3D1157%26tnum%3D1&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA51eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=cae64dcd\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=35735&amp;snA=1157&amp;tnum=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">日文攻略網</span></span>:<br />\n所有角色配技/排位/技能描述/ARK資料全部都有<br />\n<a href=\"https://altema.jp/lastcloudia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faltema.jp%2Flastcloudia%2F&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA51eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=0e27b299\" target=\"_blank\">https://altema.jp/lastcloudia/</a><br />\n<br />\nARK中文翻譯(唔齊):<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1UBnchTLnzajscsLL1zmJiq6WyKnYYx-_e0WTzgiq7Vs/htmlview#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1UBnchTLnzajscsLL1zmJiq6WyKnYYx-_e0WTzgiq7Vs%2Fhtmlview%23&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA51eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=f1ed19d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1UBnchTLnzajscsLL1zmJiq6WyKnYYx-_e0WTzgiq7Vs/htmlview#</a><br />\n<br />\n必練R/SR聖物:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vzOxuco.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvzOxuco.png&h=c076840a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/agrGnxp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FagrGnxp.png&h=5576d906&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bLaLPcr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbLaLPcr.png&h=3f8dd999&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PKLsh5O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPKLsh5O.png&h=51ee8688&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KR3JASv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKR3JASv.png&h=48bcde45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好友名單: (可自行入去更新)<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/14IN0URUbwFP9OZV000mSkKqDHO7dsyopPwdZyUzTvgw/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F14IN0URUbwFP9OZV000mSkKqDHO7dsyopPwdZyUzTvgw%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA51eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=d2b28138\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/14IN0URUbwFP9OZV000mSkKqDHO7dsyopPwdZyUzTvgw/edit#gid=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yOYoa6T.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyOYoa6T.gif&h=32341442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OFGtnAC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOFGtnAC.png&h=89b32830&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nios:<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/%E3%83%A9%E3%82%B9%E3%83%88%E3%82%AF%E3%83%A9%E3%82%A6%E3%83%87%E3%82%A3%E3%82%A2/id1439772862?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2F%25E3%2583%25A9%25E3%2582%25B9%25E3%2583%2588%25E3%2582%25AF%25E3%2583%25A9%25E3%2582%25A6%25E3%2583%2587%25E3%2582%25A3%25E3%2582%25A2%2Fid1439772862%3Fmt%3D8&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA51eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=4d4773f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/%E3%83%A9%E3%82%B9%E3%83%88%E3%82%AF%E3%83%A9%E3%82%A6%E3%83%87%E3%82%A3%E3%82%A2/id1439772862?mt=8</a><br />\n<br />\nAndroid：<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.aidis.lastcloudiajpn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.aidis.lastcloudiajpn&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA51eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=9635c349\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.aidis.lastcloudiajpn</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/7115\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.qoo-app.com%2Fapp%2F7115&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA51eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=c190320b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/7115</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jaMTfMu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjaMTfMu.png&h=d493fd84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">常用角色花名</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2/3-16/3:<br />\npool 1: pickup舊角舊ark, (冇新野)<br />\npool 2: pickup幻+LR武之帝國 (可歪出舊角舊ark)<br />\n<br />\n9/3-16/3:<br />\npool 1: pickup舊角舊ark, (冇新野)<br />\npool 2: pickup幻+LR武之帝國 (可歪出舊角舊ark)<br />\npool 3: pickup銘+LR百之夜 (可歪出舊角舊ark)"},{"pid":"25d8c4905212b976544ec1af9dd5fcdf5f15e1fb","tid":2429235,"uid":211904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:08:17.000Z","msg":"長線玩既新手買咩首抽攻略<br />\n<br />\n一般黎講呢隻GAME玩T1角+UR/絕版ARK 就夠爆GAME (可上 <a href=\"https://altema.jp/lastcloudia/charalist\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faltema.jp%2Flastcloudia%2Fcharalist&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA51eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=3d5c631d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://altema.jp/lastcloudia/charalist</a> 睇，9.5-10分角色為T1角)<br />\n<br />\n但係追求極致既話會某一D組合係勁到痴線<br />\n<br />\n以下綜合一下各連登巴吹奏角色ARK組合 同埋吹奏原因<br />\n主要係用打BOSS(高難度關)、打塔黎評價，因為暫時得呢兩樣野係難<br />\n經大量巴打重生既測試經驗，絕對中肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家吹奏的12分組合 (超勁 而且因為需求絕版角/ARK/UR ARK所以好難得到)<br />\n<br />\n- V 配 科學之燈ARK (乙太武 科學之旗)<br />\n原因: V最強普攻流可以落各種異常狀態，可以用異常單挑大部份高難度BOSS (例如死神，最終防壁，狂樹)，科學之旗大大提高普攻輸出，更容易打出頂傷，暫時普攻型V未有另一把武器有用過呢把。科燈ARK係絕版，V都係絕版，所以一定要買首抽/舊帳號先可以得到。打塔方面，除左第75層同80層不吃V既麻痺之外，其他層都係比V既麻痺狀態搞到企定定唔識郁，新手輕鬆打塔必備。另外而家PVP META暫時絕對係V玩晒，一隻未練好既V可以用異常狀態打嬴好多高練度，PVP TOP 10 人手一隻V。另外V係其中一隻可以做到2秒周回3-10實力3既角色，對於新手刷資源同老手練乙太裝都有好大幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n- 劍機 配 聖劍FF外傳ARK (學技能 聖靈藥)<br />\n原因: 兩種玩法，一種係用普攻型劍機本身有女神之吻可以用普攻吸MP，配聖靈藥扣200MP幫其他角色回技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。要求打速度既關卡可以用呢種方法幫其他角色回技(主要係幫加護回技)，而打出超快既成績。另外第2種玩法都係配聖靈藥，因為女神之吻作為永動機，可以用技能+普攻單挑大部份高難度BOSS。劍機係英雄祭角色，有機會復刻並不是絕版。聖劍FF係聖劍傳說合作ARK，暫時絕版唔知會唔會再復刻。劍機PVP算係T1角，打PVP唔需要聖靈藥，PVP TOP 10 唔少都有放劍機。<br />\n<br />\n- DANTE 配 破神大戰UR ARK(學技能 火攻增傷2)<br />\n原因: 上限好高，可單挑怕火既BOSS(狂靈樹)。DANTE本身隻野上限高，相對算硬，開完大之後物攻上限會再增加，基本上係暫時上限最頂角色之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，配埋劍聖或者紅鑽劍會再加上限更威。DANTE已經絕版，破神大戰係UR ARK非常難抽中。PVP TOP 10比較少人用DANTE，但都有。<br />\n<br />\n- 加護天使 配 破神大戰UR ARK + 最好有埋要塞UR ARK(學技能 雷攻增傷2)但非必需<br />\n原因: BLOODY PALACE最快果堆人都係用呢個組合打，而暫時黎講所有鬥快既關卡例如強敵關基本上都係靠破神加護黎打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，因為加護開大絕係會有時間停止既效果，所以會見到有d高手可以0秒就打完強敵關。科學之旗可以進一步加強加護既攻擊力，但係唔係必須，冇科燈加護可以用好多唔同既武器代替(例如 便利屋ARK、加護本身專武、機刃等等)。平時打BOSS非常萬用，基本上每隻BOSS都可以加入去打，雖然未必單挑到，但因為加護本身都係隻有女神之吻(普攻回MP)既補師，打BOSS/打塔都會好方便，又打得又補得。缺點係PVP唔算係META角，而且最基本加護同破神都並非絕版，始終想抽可以抽到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n11分組合 (都勁 但唔係絕版或者冇咁難達成)<br />\n<br />\n- 機女 + 皇龍UR ARK<br />\n超大力，可單挑死神，打大部份BOSS都可以加入既強力角色組合，打擊感手感十足，好好J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，大絕超強(配合故事精靈老頭比劍更強)，打速度關卡會用機女配合大絕快速殺敵。但唔係絕版，始終想抽未來可以抽到。PVP TOP 10 暫時唔多人用機女。<br />\n<br />\n- 大貓 + 要塞UR ARK<br />\n超勁，可單挑BLOODY PALACE，打大部份BOSS都可以加入既強力角色組合，單論血厚攻高應該全GAME第一(面板攻擊3500+ 血量12000+)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，故事本身有送專武。但唔係絕版，始終想抽未來可以抽到。PVP TOP 10 大部份人都會用大貓。<br />\n<br />\n其他有被吹奏過的強勁角色<br />\n<br />\n- 巫女<br />\n值得提一提巫女呢隻角色，唔需要配合特別既ARK，暫時最強SUPPORT，打任何BOSS關/塔關用佢都會變得簡單好多，因為佢回血可以補盾+特技都有得回血。不過打鬥快既關卡例如強敵關卡巫女係冇用。PVP META角，TOP 10都係人手放一隻巫女。<br />\n<br />\n- YODA<br />\n有招無屬性核彈魔法，打死神勁(打死神嬴左件專武就係YODA專用)，打塔可以話係最強角色。缺點係樣衰同埋PVP唔勁<br />\n<br />\n- 劍聖<br />\n主要係有一招加全隊上限2000物傷，可以再增強其他角色打既上限，本身隻角色都勁，見過有人用黎單挑死神。缺點係佬味太重同埋PVP唔勁<br />\n<br />\n- 雷姆<br />\n同劍聖一樣係無屬性輸出，本身隻角色輸出同生存能力黎講會係勁過劍聖，而且係絕左版，只不過冇劍聖全隊上限物傷能力。好J，而且PVP都算幾勁"},{"pid":"624e0800be405d2a1b2bee0829a12e9c888689f4","tid":2429235,"uid":131196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:09:18.000Z","msg":"屌你<br />\n<br />\n驚死下化<br />\n<br />\nAC拎黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a7c02749f283ca2a593865df34025d1f5c4e73","tid":2429235,"uid":211904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:09:23.000Z","msg":"不再重生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79547093a3b14afe52929da54184a9c2245d9785","tid":2429235,"uid":8023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:09:39.000Z","msg":"笑死 開錯數字"},{"pid":"c00836e32dcd9492a3787ce28d49091c41e2aa71","tid":2429235,"uid":211904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"624e0800be405d2a1b2bee0829a12e9c888689f4","tid":2429235,"uid":131196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:09:18.000Z","msg":"屌你<br />\n<br />\n驚死下化<br />\n<br />\nAC拎黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:09:44.000Z","msg":"上個post打錯咗478呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd55175030c2ea438bd3088d7b045f6b0e36ade","tid":2429235,"uid":37990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:10:10.000Z","msg":"我唔撚會推e 個嫁<br />\n下個po 個number 會正當番"},{"pid":"2c1593a7c4e11afe00d0aaffe65da9484e0f9401","tid":2429235,"uid":90549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c00836e32dcd9492a3787ce28d49091c41e2aa71","tid":2429235,"uid":211904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"624e0800be405d2a1b2bee0829a12e9c888689f4","tid":2429235,"uid":131196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T07:09:18.000Z","msg":"屌你<br 